  "body": "### What is wrong?\r\n\r\nwe have some inconsistent usage of `str` vs `pathlib.Path` for filesystem paths.\r\n\r\n\r\n### How can it be fixed\r\n\r\nMake **all** `evm/trinity/p2p` APIs return `Path` objects and downcast to `str` for all 3rd party or stdlib APIs which only support `str`\r\n",
